full_text: MAHARASHTRA 3R$50n P WINDIAS Stole CRIRT BRITH GREEN GROPER THREE RUPEES FIFTY NAYE PAISE AUG1967 357 CENTRAL START OFFICE BOMBAY to Chimanial Shah & SOLICITORS, 35, 315 BOMBAY JAP I Training ) DECLARATION We, (1) Shri Purushottam Shridhar Tendulkar, (2) Smt. Rukminibai Purushottam Tendulkar, (3) Kum. Sharayu Purushottam Tendulkar and (4) Pramod Purushottam Tendulkar, all of Bombay, Indian Inhabitants residing at 47,Tejpal Scheme, 2nd Road, Vile Parle (East) Bombay 57, India, hereby solemnly declare and say as follows: 1. I, Shri Purushottam Shridhar Tendulkar, for myself say that I have completed 66 years of my age, my date of birth being 24th July, 1901 as mentioned in my certificate of Matriculation Examination of the Bombay University, copy whereof is hereto annexed and marked Ex. "A". I have two sons, viz. Suresh alias Sureshchandra and Pramod aged respectively 34 and 22 and three daughters viz. Vimal aged 31, Sharayu aged 28 and FOIA (b)(6) as mentioned in the pedigree hereunder given. Out of three daughters, Vimal is married and FOIA (b)(6) Register No. 51 of 907
